@%*1*{: .pn}“My dear Holmes,” said I, “this is too much. You would certainly have been burned, had you lived a few centuries ago. @It is true that I had a country walk on Thursday and came home in a dreadful mess, but as I have changed my clothes I can’t imagine how you deduce it. @As to Mary Jane, she is incorrigible, and my wife has given her notice, but there, again, I fail to see how you work it out.”
